metadata.name: Before the World Ends...
metadata.description:
This piece represents the beauty of the world and computer software combined. I would feed a prompt into the computer that would try to recreate what the final moments of the earth would look like before destruction.. I was given four images, but one was not like the rest.. I would receive this beautiful piece of what looks like the exact opposite of my prompt, but it was gorgeous.

I was so thrilled to be able to make something so beautiful and capture what I felt was a perfect scene from a world that we will never know. This was not moments before disaster, but yet, moments before disruption.

This piece was made with AI (Midjourney)
